mportant}.p0-15-30{padding:0 15px 30px 15px!important}.text-footer{text-align:center!important}.m-hide,.m-td{display:none!important;width:0!important;height:0!important;font-size:0!important;line-height:0!important;min-height:0!important}.m-block{display:block!important}.fluid-img img{width:100%!important;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important}.column,.column-bottom,.column-dir,.column-empty,.column-empty2,.column-top,.column-top-30,.column-top-60{float:left!important;width:100%!important;display:block!important}.column-empty{padding-bottom:15px!important}.column-empty2{padding-bottom:30px!important}.content-spacing{width:15px!important}}</style></head><body class=\"body cui\" style=\"padding:0!important;margin:0!important;display:block!important;min-width:100%!important;width:100%!important;background:#eee;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none\"><table bgcolor=\"#eaf2f2\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:25px 0\" valign=\"top\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"mobile-shell\" width=\"650\"><tr><td class=\"td\" style=\"width:650px;min-width:650px;font-size:0;line-height:0;padding:0;margin:0;font-weight:400\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td class=\"p30-15 img-center\" style=\"padding:30px 0 15px 0;font-size:0;line-height:0;text-align:left\"><a href=\"#\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"netacadLogo\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"50\" src=\"https://netacad.com/skillsforall/img/email/netacadLogo.png\" style=\"height:35px!important\" width=\"\"></a></td></tr></table><table bgcolor=\"#ebebeb\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" class=\"p30-15-0\" style=\"padding:30px 30px 15px 30px;border-radius:15px 15px 0 0\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:25px\">Well done Marwan.!</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:15px\">Excellent work on successfully completing <span style=\"font-weight:700\">Networking Devices and Initial Configuration</span> course. It’s a great accomplishment and a powerful step towards new and exciting opportunities.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-top:15px\">You’ve Earned a Digital Badge</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px;padding-top:15px\">Show others this significant achievement by sharing your badge on social media and professional networks. Follow the steps below to claim your digital badge:</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px\"><ol start=\"1\"><li>Go to our partner website: <a href=\"https://www.credly.com/badges/0839d6e3-ec56-4075-a8f1-fa791c3fa108/accept\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#53bae6;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700\">Claim my badge</span></a></li></ol></td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px\"><ol start=\"2\"><li>Use your email from this message to create an account or sign in with your existing account.</li></ol></td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px\"><ol start=\"3\"><li>Once logged in, select the <span style=\"font-weight:700\">Networking Devices and Initial Configuration</span> badge, then select Accept.</li></ol></td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px\"><ol start=\"4\"><li>You can then share your digital badge via email or social media.</li></ol></td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px\"><ol start=\"5\"><li>You also have the option of downloading a printable certificate when you share your badge publicly. Find out more about <a href=\"https://support.credly.com/hc/en-us/articles/360026639872-Can-I-download-and-print-my-badge-certificate-\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#53bae6;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700\">downloading and printing a badge</span>.</a></li></ol></td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-top:15px\">Keep Moving Forward</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px;padding-top:15px\">Continue to build on your success by exploring more courses and resources in the Learning Catalog on NetAcad.com.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px;padding-top:20px\">This accomplishment is just the beginning. We are confident in your potential and excited to see the amazing things you will achieve.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#495057;font-weight:300;font-size:16px;line-height:22px;text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px;padding-top:20px\"><p>Cheering you on,</p><p>The Cisco Networking Academy Team</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table bgcolor=\"#ebebeb\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#025073\" class=\"p30-15-0\" style=\"padding:30px 30px 15px 30px;border-radius:0 0 15px 15px\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td style=\"text-align:center;padding-bottom:20px\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cisconetworkingacademy/\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#fff;text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"margin-right:10px;cursor:pointer\"><img alt=\"facebook\" src=\"https://netacad.com/skillsforall/img/email/facebook.png\"></span></a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLA48B49E7FB15439B\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#fff;text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"margin-right:10px;cursor:pointer\"><img alt=\"yoyutube\" src=\"https://netacad.com/skillsforall/img/email/youtube.png\"></span></a><a href=\"https://x.com/CiscoNetAcad\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#fff;text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"margin-right:10px;cursor:pointer\"><img alt=\"x\" src=\"https://netacad.com/skillsforall/img/email/x.png\"></span></a><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/school/cisco-networking-academy1/\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#fff;text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"margin-right:10px;cursor:pointer\"><img alt=\"linkedIn\" src=\"https://netacad.com/skillsforall/img/email/linkedIn.png\"></span></a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#fff;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;text-align:center;padding-bottom:15px\">Join Cisco Networking Academy feeds to be the first to hear about updates and opportunities, and share your own innovative ideas.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#fff;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;text-align:center;padding-bottom:10px\">Please do not reply to this email.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#fff;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;text-align:center;padding-bottom:10px\">To update your preferences or unsubscribe, log into <a href=\"https://netacad.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:underline;color:#fff\" target=\"_blank\">NetAcad.com</a>, click on your profile in the top right corner, and update your Communication Opt-In preference.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#fff;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;text-align:center;padding-bottom:10px\">©2025   Cisco Systems, Inc. and/or its affiliates. All rights reserved. 170 W Tasman, San Jose, CA 95134.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:CiscoSans,Arial,sans-serif;color:#fff;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;text-align:center;padding-bottom:10px\"><span style=\"border-right:1px solid #fff;margin-right:10px;padding-right:10px\"><a href=\"https://www.cisco.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#fff\" target=\"_blank\">Cisco.com</a></span><span style=\"border-right:1px solid #fff;margin-right:10px;padding-right:10px\"><a href=\"https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/about/legal/privacy.html\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#fff\" target=\"_blank\">Privacy Statement</a></span><span><a href=\"https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/about/legal/trademarks.html\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#fff\" target=\"_blank\">Trademarks</a></span></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
